import './style.css'
import { Form, FormGroup, Input, Button } from 'reactstrap';

const form = () => {

  return (

    <Form className="wrapper">

      <FormGroup className="search-wrapper">
        <section class="search-box">
          <Input
            id="typeSearch"
            name="search"
            placeholder="Type of Therapy"
            type="search"
          />
          <Input
            id="suburbSearch"
            name="search"
            placeholder="Suburb or Postcode"
            type="search"
          />
          <Button
            color="success"
            active size="lg"
          >
            Search
          </Button>
        </section>
      </FormGroup>
    </Form>

  )
}
export default form
